result.formatted_address: Clarence Terrace, Sai Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: The Big Bite Flame Grill

reviews.text: Caesar salad is only lettuce and dressing. You can have the same quality Caesar salad in McDonald’s. What was worse is that they forgot our main course, so we asked about that and then it came really fast: chicken was charred on the outside but bloody and cold on the inside. Disappointed. We asked for the check, went home and cooked some pasta of our own. [Edit: check out the owner's response in the attached screen cap]

Worst service!
The waitresses/waiter just hiding behind the cashier table and playing phones.
Even if we yelled they wont bother us unless we walked to the counter.

And when they responded to customers, they showed an annoying face. 
With this price I could really go somewhere with better service and food.
Wont come again for sure!

Delicious Canadian food 🥂👍 we ordered Poutine and chicken tenders. We got free beers today with the Poutine. Service are good. polite and helpful! Explained the menu to us. Coz we never been here!' but too many mosquitoes there.
Great food with reasonable price

Ive been here many times. The food is ok. Tastes like backyard burger, nothing to complain or rave over.

The issue is with the staff. They are rather unattentive, indifferent, apathetic, and sometimes will pout or sigh when you ask them what happened to your order that was sent in over 40 minutes ago, which is the second issue with this place. On multiple occasions theyve messed up my order... sometimes food portion comes out less than usual too for some reason.

Overall not the worst place I've ever been.
